trans-unit.source: Specifies the visual state of a track bar slider (also known as a thumb) that is drawn with visual styles.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o estado visual de um controle barra controle deslizante (também conhecido como uma miniatura) que é desenhado com estilos visuais.

trans-unit.source: The TrackBarThumbState values correspond to the states of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement> objects exposed by the following classes: - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.Thumb> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbBottom> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbLeft> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbRight> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbTop> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbVertical> The TrackBarThumbState values are also used as an argument in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TrackBarRenderer?displayProperty=fullName> class methods that draw the track bar slider.
trans-unit.target: Os valores de TrackBarThumbState correspondem aos estados do <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement>expostos pelas classes de objetos:- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.Thumb>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbBottom>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbLeft>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbRight>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbTop>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbVertical>TrackBarThumbState os valores também são usados como um argumento no <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TrackBarRenderer?displayProperty=fullName>classe métodos que desenhar o controle deslizante barra de trilha.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TrackBarRenderer?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbVertical> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbTop> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbRight> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbLeft> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.ThumbBottom> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.TrackBar.Thumb> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement>
